about api

Api folder directory : app/Api

#### FILTERS ####

Filters directory : app/Api/Filters

using filters we can order or filter our data

each controller need to each filter

#### REPOSITORIES ####

Repositories directory :  app/Api/Repositories

using repositories we can return some model

each model need to each repository

#### TRANSFORMERS ####

Repositories directory :  app/Api/Transformers

using transformers we can create mutation for our response

each service need to use each transformer

#### SERVICES ####

Repositories directory :  app/Api/Services

using services we can create response
    1. set select
    2. set relations
    3. overwrite some functions

each controller need to use each service

